snippet.title: Frogger in toy town : Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Toppling blocks, falling books...
Things that seem unimportant to humans can pose great danger in the frog world...
Frogger is back! The classic frog-action game returns on Apple Arcade with an all-new look and the same simple gameplay. 
Guide the iconic amphibian forward as you evade the numerous obstacles in your path!

Take your first little leap into a huge adventure!

https://www.konami.com/games/frogger/tt/
